  "referralShareMessage": "Try Shubhmilan — meaningful connections for the diaspora.\n\nDownload the app here: {link}\n\nWhen you sign up, enter my referral code: {code}\n\nYou get 30 days free Premium (India only). Plus, top referrers can win up to ₹1,00,000 every month!",
